{"tid":2368311,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"下代 iPhone 名字   竟然唔係 iPhone 13","createTime":"2021-01-16T05:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T03:01:11.000Z","uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"43d0a626e50c74c832d760892c74d790759b231c","tid":2368311,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:40:43.000Z","msg":"仲係M額?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年發表的 iPhone 12 系列，縱使是首批支援 5G 的 iPhone，但已經吸引了眾多消費者入手。不過很多人還是對下一代 iPhone 抱有期望，因為有傳聞指 Apple 打算改用 LTPO 螢幕，而且所有型號都同時支援。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有很多人認為下一代 iPhone 將會稱為 iPhone 13，但網站 cnet 引述消息人士指 Apple 可能會將之命名為。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。以往 Apple 都曾經推出過「S」系列 iPhone，例如 iPhone 4s、iPhone 5s 和 iPhone 6s 等，有指命名為 iPhone 12s 的原因亦與。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n <br />\n該名爆料人士又提到 iPhone 12s 系列其中一項主要變化，就是螢幕 M 字額面積會縮小。因為 Apple 會以 D-ToF（Direct ToF）技術取代現有的 Face ID 組件，由於體積減少，所以令為人詬病的 M 字額有望縮小。<br />\n <br />\n資料來源：gizchina<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/217571/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4544%2F217571%2F1%2F&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=ecfbcd4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/217571/1/</a>"},{"pid":"775f243c3849b92dfced4b8c100e3dfbd2a27706","tid":2368311,"uid":25754,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:43:39.000Z","msg":"竟然咁大膽敢改個咁嘅名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef25fc14e45dffd9ceca81f0383b7c503b39bd25","tid":2368311,"uid":77474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:44:16.000Z","msg":"直接15 算啦"},{"pid":"943d90684baf32b2f1798668f66caf9b7857c91f","tid":2368311,"uid":25656,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"quote":{"pid":"775f243c3849b92dfced4b8c100e3dfbd2a27706","tid":2368311,"uid":25754,"like":13